HEADWORD: blastomycosis
<hw>blastomycosis</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>any of several fungal
infections caused by blastomycetes; they are characterized by
inflammatory lesions of skin and mucous membranes or internal
organs.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>blastomycotic</ent>⟦br⟧
